<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="advocate-vt">advocate <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ædvəkeɪt/    美 /'ædvəkeɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>提倡；拥护；主张：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>advocate (sb) doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Many experts advocate rewarding your child for good behaviour. 
很多专家提倡对孩子的良好表现加以奖励。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>advocate + that … (should) do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The leader advocates that each member (should) play their part.
领导主张每个成员都发挥各自的作用。</p></div></div>